1
00:00:04,004 --> 00:00:07,076
Thanks to the hard work of interns and contributors
感谢各位实习生和贡献者的辛苦工作

2
00:00:07,078 --> 00:00:09,566
GNOME announce the version 3.18
GNOME 正式发布 3.18 版本

3
00:00:10,016 --> 00:00:15,952
In this release GNOME improves the general user experience for users and new developers alike
在这个版本中，GNOME 为普通用户和新开发者提升了用户体验

4
00:00:17,002 --> 00:00:19,295
If you computer has a light sensor
如果你的电脑有光线传感器

5
00:00:19,298 --> 00:00:23,684
GNOME can now use it automatically adjust the brightness of your screen
GNOME 现在可以使用它自动来调节你的屏幕的亮度

6
00:00:24,008 --> 00:00:29,419
the touchscreen experience has also improved when selecting and modifying text
触摸屏提升了选择和修改文本的体验

7
00:00:30,076 --> 00:00:33,854
"Files" has received a lot of attention this cycle
这个版本的“文件管理器”也有了大量改变

8
00:00:34,032 --> 00:00:36,153
there's a new view in the sidebar
侧边栏有了新的视图风格

9
00:00:36,158 --> 00:00:40,634
so remote and internal locations are collected in one place for your convenience
远程和内部位置放在一起以便操作

10
00:00:40,742 --> 00:00:45,000
Progress is now shown in the header bar when files are being copy
当文件复制的时候顶部也会显示进度条

11
00:00:45,004 --> 00:00:47,415
There are many other improvements
还有很多其他改进

12
00:00:47,418 --> 00:00:50,224
inlcuding  a more polished search function,
包括了更细腻的搜索体验、

13
00:00:50,228 --> 00:00:52,500
Google Drive integration
集成了 Google Drive

14
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:54,682
and better file management.
以及更好的文件管理。

15
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:01,741
"Software" has become the first suport updating device firmware
“软件”首先支持设备固件的更新

16
00:01:01,748 --> 00:01:04,992
use new Linux Vendor firmware service
通过新的 Linux 厂商固件服务程序。

17
00:01:05,048 --> 00:01:08,080
The service allows vendors to submit firmware
这个服务支持厂家提交固件

18
00:01:08,289 --> 00:01:12,074
and GNOME Software allow allow you to install it with the click of a button
GNOME 软件程序将允许你一键安装固件

19
00:01:14,024 --> 00:01:19,249
Further more, the GNOME community has improved a large variety of Apps.
同时，GNOME 社区也完善了大量应用程序，

20
00:01:19,259 --> 00:01:20,759
including "Calendar"
包括"日历”

21
00:01:20,769 --> 00:01:25,426
which now comes with a management dialog to help you manage your calendars.
现在有了一个管理对话框来帮助你管理日历。

22
00:01:25,436 --> 00:01:26,819
Polari
Polari (IRC 客户端)

23
00:01:26,829 --> 00:01:29,141
with a better initially user experience.
有了更好的初始化用户体验。

24
00:01:29,151 --> 00:01:31,579
GNOME Documents
GNOME 文档

25
00:01:31,589 --> 00:01:35,898
which is supporting a revamped user interface for organizing your documents.
现在支持改变用户界面以更好的组织文档

26
00:01:35,908 --> 00:01:37,943
And Evince
还有 Evince (pdf 文件阅读器)

27
00:01:37,948 --> 00:01:39,822
which annotation and video support has improved.
提升了注解和对视频的支持。

28
00:01:43,219 --> 00:01:46,440
GNOME 3.18 comes with a preview of the GNOME To Do
GNOME 3.18 还包括了预览版的 GNOME To Do

29
00:01:46,672 --> 00:01:50,875
a personal task manager helping you keep track of the tasks ahead of time.
一款个人任务管理工具，帮助你跟踪任务和规划时间

30
00:01:52,277 --> 00:01:55,681
GNOME development tools have also improved in this cycles
这个版本对 GNOME 的开发工具也有了提升

31
00:01:55,781 --> 00:01:57,283
Builder for example
例如 Builder (GNOME 集成开发环境)

32
00:01:57,383 --> 00:01:59,350
now has a source code minimap
现在有了查看源代码的快捷键minimap

33
00:01:59,358 --> 00:02:00,929
a shortcut overview
一个快捷键预览

34
00:02:01,138 --> 00:02:02,787
and an auto completion for Python
以及 Python 语言的自动完成功能

35
00:02:03,028 --> 00:02:06,688
the Human Interface Guidelines have been restructured
用户界面规则也重新规划了

36
00:02:06,698 --> 00:02:09,311
and including new usage pattern.
增加了新的使用模式。

37
00:02:09,321 --> 00:02:12,957
GNOME Logs user interface now goes better overview
GNOME Logs 的用户界面有了更好的预览

38
00:02:13,050 --> 00:02:15,534
I can show you logs from the last five boots.
可以显示最后 5 次启动的日志。

39
00:02:16,024 --> 00:02:18,692
Boxes has improved interface
Boxes 也改进了界面

40
00:02:18,698 --> 00:02:19,668
with the new list view
有了新的列表视图

41
00:02:19,678 --> 00:02:22,129
for users with a lot of virtual machines.
方便有大量虚拟机的用户。

42
00:02:22,229 --> 00:02:26,308
Finally GTK+ has received new typographic features
最后，GTK+ 有了新的字体特性

43
00:02:28,028 --> 00:02:30,651
A new GNOME relase is available for you
你现在可以获得新版 GNOME

44
00:02:30,661 --> 00:02:33,555
as a live image to try now.
它是一个 live 版的镜像
（视频中的地址有误，可访问上一级目录查看）

45
00:02:34,089 --> 00:02:37,593
Many distributions will also ship  GNOME 3.18 in the near future.
很多发行版都会在未来搭载 GNOME 3.18。

46
00:02:39,036 --> 00:02:43,491
GNOME is a friendly community making free software for everyone.
GNOME 是一个为每个人构建自由软件的友好社区。

47
00:02:43,591 --> 00:02:45,047
Excited?
心动了？

48
00:02:45,147 --> 00:02:49,296
join us in making the perfect desktop environment!
加入我们让 GNOME 成为完美的桌面环境！

